Re: Hiragana Times article: 草食系男子, 肉食系男子
by katafei » Wed 09.09.2009 3:08 pm There is also a play one the wordt 'vegetarian' that refers to people who are always sitting cross-legged on the floor....but I can't remember it exactly...
